data.description: Rarely available waterfront 5.72-acre treasure atop a bluff on the Island's sunny west side with breathtaking views of the Olympic Mountains, whales, and other wildlife. Main cottage & separate potentially income-producing ADU/guest house are encircled by majestic evergreens, lawn, and plenty of sunshine to soak up on a new deck. A tree-lined path leads to area wide enough for a house near the bluff, staircase to dock and uncommon sandy beach below. Property features massive pavilion, detached garage, and a feeling you will not find anywhere else. Drive to your island retreat; no ferry needed. Discover the epitome of privacy and calm with this exceptional property.
